  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "What if I only want specific accounts visible to DApps, would it be worth it to have a CLI param for this? Perhaps something like: 'geth --visible=\"0,3,4\"' (where 0, 3, 4 are accounts 0, 3 and 4). The reason is that some DApps will have full access to all user accounts, some users may not want specific accounts to be in anyway related to others that they own (i.e. they have some private and some public accounts). This is mainly a practical privacy concern.\n",
